resourceTemplates.name: typecast-list-voices-v2
resourceTemplates.title: Typecast - List Voices (V2)
resourceTemplates.description: Lists all available Typecast voice models with enhanced metadata and model-grouped emotion support. Supports optional filtering by TTS model (ssfm-v30 or ssfm-v21), gender (male, female), age group (child, teenager, young_adult, middle_age, elder), and use case category (Announcer, Anime, Audiobook, Conversational, Documentary, E-learning, Rapper, Game, Tiktok/Reels, News, Podcast, Voicemail, Ads). Returns voices including voice_id, voice_name, supported model versions with emotion sets, gender, age group, and tagged use cases. Requires X-API-KEY header.
